Name: frmProjects Purpose: Add/edit projects

Fields to Include:

ProjectName (Text)
BuildingAddress (Text)
City (Text)
State (Combo - linked to lookup)
ZipCode (Text)
ClientOrgID (Combo - Organizations table)
ProjectStatus (Combo - Lookup table)
StartDate (Date)
EndDate (Date)
BudgetAmount (Currency)
ProjectManager (Text)
TotalUnits (Number)
